## Validation Rules

Before ANY write:
- [ ] Required fields are present (see schema.yaml)
- [ ] Foreign keys reference existing records
- [ ] Enum values are valid
- [ ] last_updated = today
- [ ] No duplicate PKs
- [ ] Date format is YYYY-MM-DD
- [ ] Text fields do not start with = + - @ (CSV injection prevention)

